@item --with lis
@opindex  lis

When enabled, @dfn{STREAMS} add-on packages will also have RedHat RPMs or Debian DEBs built for the
@cite{Linux STREAMS} (@command{LiS-@value{VERSION_LIS}}) @dfn{STREAMS} package.  @samp{--with LIS}
must also be specified.
The default is to not build RPMs nor DEBs for @cite{LiS} version of the add-on @dfn{STREAMS}
packages.
As @cite{LiS} is deprecated, so is this option.

@item --without lfs
@opindex lfs

