@cite{Linux Fast-STREAMS} (@command{streams-@value{VERSION_STREAMS}}) package.  @samp{--without
STREAMS} may also be specified.
The default is to build RPMs nor DEBs for @cite{Linux Fast-STREAMS} version of the add-on
@dfn{STREAMS} packages.
As @cite{LiS} is deprecated, and this option is only useful for suppressing @cite{Linux
Fast-STREAMS} builds in favour of @cite{LiS}, this option is also deprecated.

